==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: disabling
<hw>disabling</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>causing or having
caused disability; rendering disabled; <as>as, <ex>disabling</ex>
injury</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> crippling, incapacitating.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>depriving of legal right; rendering legally
disqualified; <as>as, certain <ex>disabling</ex> restrictions
disqualified him for citizenship</as>.</def> <ant>enabling</ant>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> disqualifying.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>disabuse</ent>⟦br⟧
